Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:20.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}冷たい夜の入り口で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:30.06,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}うつむき　まちぶせ　やっと出会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:36.73,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}ふたりきり　だれにも知られず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:44.17,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}お願いよ　離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:51.28,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}ほほそめて照れる赤い風船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.48,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can say… I can say…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:59.23,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can never say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:06.63,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}夢では何度告げたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:10.47,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can say… I can say…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:14.66,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can never say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:20.36,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あなたに伝わるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.59,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Let me love you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:13.37,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}黑暗抹去了晚霞的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:20.81,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}在寒夜的入口处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:30.06,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}低下头  默默等待  直到你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:36.73,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}在这无人的角落  就只有你跟我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:44.17,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}求求你  别离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:51.28,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}双颊让夕阳的余光染得绯红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.48,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can say…  I can say…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:59.23,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can never say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:06.63,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}尽管已在梦中无数次地告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:10.47,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can say…  I can say…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:14.66,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I can never say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:20.36,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}总有一天要将这份感念传达给你
